{"tid":1161791,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭恩地來港最恨食點心","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T05:36:50.000Z","uid":160973,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2938413bccccac3f8e589427a1ca9d5662e68cd","tid":1161791,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"你睇下人地都係用廣東話同特登用中文歌<br />\n<br />\n甫出場，恩地先用廣東話跟港迷打招呼：「大家好，我係恩地！」續說聽到很多粉絲叫得非常大聲嚇一大跳，又多謝粉絲支持，將原本一場的演出加至兩場，不過這次恩地坦言沒有特別準備廣東歌，明晚只會演唱《Being There》的國語版本，又承諾下次必定會練廣東歌回饋粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2w8Qi4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2w8Qi4Q&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPaix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=b5d3d695\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2w8Qi4Q</a>"},{"pid":"8ca9f3323b02fb823d247aa20b4fcea3bb04a733","tid":1161791,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"邊位愚樂台Ching??<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/58ff9a4d-da04-46f9-8025-ac7273d85aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fentertainment%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F58ff9a4d-da04-46f9-8025-ac7273d85aa5.jpg&h=eca31921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3c85ff1fa2b16e679f01423078967bef6f09cd4","tid":1161791,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f02eabcc0c675dc8d5ef46100477b27445c05c","tid":1161791,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ca9f3323b02fb823d247aa20b4fcea3bb04a733","tid":1161791,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"邊位愚樂台Ching??<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/58ff9a4d-da04-46f9-8025-ac7273d85aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.co